.TH CPPTEST 1 "February 2026" "4.1" "CppTest Manual"
.SH NAME
cpptest \- Advanced competitive programming testing utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cpptest
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fIFILE\fR] [\fIDIRECTORY\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Automated testing tool for C++. Supports test generation, stress testing, isolation, custom checkers, clang-tidy, and multiple compilers.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-g ", " \-\-gen-only
\fBGenerate Only.\fR Compiles \fIgen.cpp\fR, generates tests into \fIgen_tests/\fR, and exits without running solutions.
.TP
.BR \-S ", " \-\-stress
\fBStress Mode.\fR Requires \fIfast.cpp\fR and \fIgen.cpp\fR. Runs an infinite loop.
.TP
.BR \-R ", " \-\-no-comments
\fBRemove Comments.\fR \fBWARNING:\fR Permanently removes comments from \fImain.cpp\fR and exits.
.TP
.BR \-G ", " \-\-no-gen-config
Ignore \fItests.cfg\fR file.
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-in-place
Run tests directly in the source directory.
.TP
.BR \-F ", " \-\-fix
\fBAuto-Fix Mode.\fR Automatically applies style fixes.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-fast
Skip static analysis.
.TP
.BR \-K ", " \-\-force-checker
Force usage of \fIcheck.cpp\fR.
.TP
.BR \-k ", " \-\-force-diff
Force usage of standard diff.
.TP
.BR \-u ", " \-\-update
Self-update from GitHub.
